Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.68,Gen_Italics,ruby,0,0,0,,11:30, reunión de\N{\i0}¡Excava hondo! ¡¡Con olfato canino!!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.10,Gen_Italics,ruby,0,0,0,,12:00, grabo un reportaje.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:51.43,Gen_Italics,ruby,0,0,0,,15:00, me desplazo y como.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:55.62,Gen_Italics,ruby,0,0,0,,Reviso la entrevista\Ny estudio para los finales.
